Title: Eon's Fringe
Description:
Timewalker Tempo and their team finally unfroze Eon's Fringe!

Er... mostly. The Timewalkers have things more or less under control but Eon's Fringe has some problems the people of the town wouldn't mind a hand with. 

Tell Bob I sent ya!
ObjectivesText: Find Bartender Bob in Eon's Fringe.
